w Roman'; font-size:11pt">tions under international law  are being dishonoured by the new Legal Aid rules. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">At the current rate the ‘Big Society’ is shrinking to quite a small ‘Good Society’ as statutory resources are being </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">withheld from more</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and more areas of migrant lives, whilst </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">obstructing their ability to contribute to our society</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> economically and culturally</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">8</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">.) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">a)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">+ b): a)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">The effects on those who arrived with a valid visa to work and found their work was abusive, </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">their study </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">not as agreed, or even non-existent</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> E</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">xamples </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size